1.title: The Creeps/From Bad to Worse
1.plot: The Creeps: Finn and Jake receive an invitation to a masquerade dinner. / From Bad to Worse: A zombie epidemic strikes in Ooo... and it's Princess Bubblegum's fault.

2.title: In the House/Death Metal Crash Pit/Creepy Doll
2.plot: In the House: Rigby eggs the wrong house and gets cursed by a wizard. / Death Metal Crash Pit: Muscle Man and High Five Ghost want to crash an old RV into a pit. / Creepy Doll: Mordecai and Rigby discover an old Victorian Doll.

3.title: Halloween/The Ghost
3.plot: Halloween: Carrie takes Gumball, Darwin and Anais to a real haunted house party on Halloween! / The Ghost: Gumball must learn to say "no" when Carrie the Ghost uses his body against his will.

4.title: Death Bear/Ello Gov'nor
4.plot: Death Bear: Mordecai and Rigby want to get a picture in death bear's cage to impress Margaret and Eileen. / Ello Gov'nor: The guys have to help Rigby overcome his fears.

5.title: It Came from the Nightosphere/Death in Bloom
5.plot: It Came From the Nightsophere: Finn must defeat the Lord of Evil while attempting to reunite him with his daughter, Marceline. / Death in Bloom: Finn and Jake have to go on a quest to replace Princess Bubblegum's rare flower.

imdb.plot outline: We've got zombies, ghosts, and creepy dolls who wanna draw on your face! With Cartoon Network's FRIGHTPASS, you have access to the spookiest episodes of your favorite Cartoon Network shows! You'll laugh, you'll scream, you'll try to convince everyone that you totally weren't even scared at all!
